        Any $* command will fail, should not send them after sending a command
    Fix sync command G4 sometimes failing when jogging: "g-code locked out during alarm or jog state"
    Fix: sometimes status messages stop coming through and no command works anymore.
    InputFields
        When it looses focus, the entered value is not applied
    When one of the workers fail, UI hangs, it does not exit
